  "Weekly": "每周",
  "Welcome to the SDL Onsite Course!\nThis program equips you with the skills to recognize and respond to cardiac emergencies involving adults, childs, and infants through comprehensive training and hands-on practice. \n\nBefore staring, ensure you’ve reviewed the course outline and prepared to engage in each step, from instructional videos to practical sessions. \n\nUpon successful completion, you’ll receive a 2-year digital certificate to validate your achievement. \n\nLet’s get started and build your life-saving skills!": "欢迎参加SDL现场培训课程！\n该课程旨在通过全面的理论培训和实践练习，帮助您掌握识别和应对成人、儿童和婴儿心脏骤停紧急情况所需的技能。\n\n在开始学习之前，请查看课程概述，\n并做好准备积极参与从培训视频到实践课程的每一个步骤。\n\n成功完成课程后，您将获得一份有效期为两年的数字证书，以证明您的成绩。\n\n现在就开始积累这项拯救生命的宝贵技能吧！",
